Hi Professor Tony,

Regarding the Corpus integration, I spoke with Enoh and learned that the =
current NotebookLM, Perplexity Space, and GPTs with corpus haven=E2=80=99t=
 been shared with users yet.

Is there a plan to explore these AI spaces to users for feedback to help =
improve them further?

Since users may not know how to formulate questions initially if we only =
provide a chatbox, one idea in my mind is to provide users with =
categorized questions they can click to generate queries in Perplexity =
Space and view up-to-date results. We could also create pre-generated =
pages for these questions.

